snippet.title: Genshin Funkin' (Friday Night Funkin' Mod Showcase)
snippet.description:
Go Play the Mod!:
https://gamebanana.com/mods/339310
https://gamejolt.com/games/genshinfunkin/667793

Dragonspine Deviatin' Update: https://youtu.be/tN_09qJnbHA
Version 2.5 Update: https://youtu.be/t6iUY_KV0tM

Timestamps:
00:00 Disclaimer
00:22 Title Screen
00:45 Liyue Funkin'
00:56 Koguchi Monou
04:20 Let the Wind Tell You (COPYRIGHT)
08:08 Hikaru Nara (COPYRIGHT)
12:26 Inazuma Rockin'
12:34 Renai Circulation (COPYRIGHT)
16:51 Saikai
20:57 Vigilant Yaksha
24:08 Mondstadt Balladin'
24:19 Bloom of the Wind
27:24 Heaven's Map
32:05 Soldier, Poet, King (COPYRIGHT)
35:25 Celestial Destiny Remastered (Bonus Track)
36:58 Hu Tao Sings Endless v1 (Bonus Track)
40:01 Credits
41:55 Outro

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Mod Description:
Travel around the world of Teyvat as Hu-Tao, as you challenge others in a sing off. With 3 full weeks featuring fan songs and covers sung by some of the original Genshin voice actors! This was made as a tribute to the incredible talents of the Genshin voice actors. Includes easy and normal difficulties respectively, along with swapped charts to play the opponent’s side!

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Songs Used In Order of Appearance (please go check them out!):

A Sweet Smile Groove [Instrumental] (Genshin Impact Remix) | Miloh: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UXTBxeWyuU8

胡口桃生 (Hu Tao) (English Version) | PeachyFranny feat. Raayo: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8za2EYuDcjE

Let the Wind Tell You | 花园花玲, 喵☆酱, 宴宁ccccc, and kinsen: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KrNUrgaOsCc

Hikaru Nara | 多多, kinsen, 花玲, 喵酱, 小N, 宴宁, 鹿喑, and 萧翟: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eF6preXfMHw

Renai Circulation | kinsen & 鹿喑kana: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1YrI0y1yG_0

Saikai | kinsen & 鹿喑kana: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hHoBogOuxhw

Vigilant Yaksha | kinsen: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q7x746k_lM0

Bloom of the Wind | VA Singers are displayed on the video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GeMIsH3XUuc

Heaven's Map | 多多poi and 宴宁ccccc: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uHW9NMedm8A

Soldier, Poet, King (Venti Version from "Genshin Impact") | Joe Zieja and Erika Harlacher: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VTiqVG1qs7M

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Credits:

Gamenwatch412 | Main Coder & Charter, & cover maker for Celestial Destiny & Endless: 
Forums: http://thegamenwatchforums.weebly.com/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/gamenwatch412

Doodle | Artist for Aether sprite, creator credit icons and Inazuma background (Google Draw): https://discordapp.com/users/772212603857403904/

Minja | Storywriter / Tester: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC1bs54iU3nxb1i-MH9H6MSQ

Rainbow1225: Moral and mental support: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCPk5BmcnOj-zPJlz14_Inog

RedFlaim | Creator of Hu-Tao, Chongyun, Xingqiu sprites and Liyue background: https://gamebanana.com/members/1873543

Kurxmi | Creator of Keqing and Kaeya sprites: https://gamebanana.com/members/1837776

Fenveon | Creator of Venti sprite: https://gamebanana.com/members/1775140

Shadow Mario | Psych Engine Creator: https://gamebanana.com/members/1735892

MarStarBro | Original Composer for Endless (Sonic.exe): https://gamebanana.com/members/1966168

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The complete Genshin Funkin’ voicebanks are provided as well as well as the original samples, and MIDIs, in case you want to use them in your BETADCIUs. Includes chromatics for Albedo, Aether, Hu-Tao, Childe, Keqing, Raiden Shogun, Venti, and Zhongli! Remember to credit me for the voicebanks.

https://github.com/gamenwatch412/Genshin-Funkin-Voicebanks

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

No copyright infringement intended.

#FridayNightFunkin #FNF #GenshinImpact
